      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in pristine, showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated to the most exacting standards, preserving its original aesthetic luster and mechanical integrity. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands uncompromising excellence and a flawless driving experience. Every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous care, ensuring this motorcar remains an investment-grade asset.",
