      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute beauty. It has been pampered like a member of the family and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014seriously, not a scratch or a speck out of place! It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for total perfection, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 47500.0,
