    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54B32 power plant features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a pristine chassis, free of any structural fatigue. Every bushing, gasket, and fluid has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension deliver telepathic handling. This is a collector-grade example with flawless paint depth and a showroom-fresh interior.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
