      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirls. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, showing zero curb rash, and are wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber. Step inside to find an interior that still retains its original showroom scent. The premium leather seats are supple with no cracking or bolster wear, and every tactile surface feels as crisp as the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive paper trail to prove it. Always garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather, the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
